# Playwright artifact-typed catch-alls scoped to where they actually appear.
# A blanket `*.png` / `*.html` would shadow tracked files like the Vite
# entry index.html or future favicons. The artifact directories are already
# gitignored above (playwright-report/, .playwright-mcp/, test-results/,
# smoke-report/), so no top-level type-based rule is needed.
